cs.SI, cs.SOC, cs.HC, cs.IR, cs.CL 

The paper focuses on understanding the browsing and voting behavior of individuals on social news websites, specifically Reddit. This falls under the category of social media and online communities (cs.SOC) and human-computer interaction (cs.HC). The study also involves analyzing the content of the website, which could fall under information retrieval (cs.IR) and natural language processing (cs.CL). Finally, the paper discusses the dataset and the methods used for analysis, which could fall under social network analysis (cs.SI).
